query:
SELECT p.id, p.title, p.headline, COUNT(pi.id) as image_count 
FROM properties p 
LEFT JOIN propertyImages pi ON p.id = pi.propertyId 
GROUP BY p.id 
ORDER BY image_count DESC 
LIMIT 5;
